<h1>What would you most like feedback on?</h1>
<p>Since this is an early draft, some parts may be more "under-construction" than others. Help your classmates focus what they give you feedback on. Select which rubric items you need most help with. </p>

<ul class="rubric" style="display:inline;">
  <% @answer.assignment.rubric_items.each do |r| %>
    <div class="col-xs-6">
      <li class="selectable-rubric">
        <div class="row-fluid">
          <button class="btn btn-default need-help btn-block">I want feedback on this item
          <%= "(Recommended)" if r.show_for_feedback? %>
          <%= "- not used for final grades" if !r.show_for_final? %>
          </button>
        </div>
        <legend></legend>
        <div class="row-fluid">
          <div class="col-sm-11"><strong><%= r.short_title%></strong></div>
          <span class="badge col-sm-1"><%=r.max_label%></span>
        </div>
        <div class="row-fluid">
          <%=r.title %>
        </div>
        <div class="row-fluid form-inline" id="checkboxes-<%=r.id%>">
          <% r.answer_attributes.each do |a| %>
            <div class="fields row-fluid">
              <div class="form-group" style="width: 75%;"><input type="checkbox" disabled="disabled"> <%= a.description%></div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </li>    
    </div>
  <% end %>
</ul>
<div class="col-sm-6">
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="request">Any special requests for your reviewers?</label>
    <textarea class="form-control" placeholder="Can you tell me if I am going in the right direction for..."></textarea>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="actions">        
  <div class="navbar-right">
    <%= link_to "Cancel reviewing", edit_answer_path, :class=>"btn btn-danger", :role=>"button" %>
    <%= link_to "Get feedback on draft", submit_for_feedback_answer_path, :class=>"btn btn-success", :role=>"button", :method=>:post %>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
  $(function() {
      $('.need-help').click(function() {
        $(this).closest('.selectable-rubric').toggleClass('alert-success');
        $(this).find('input[type="checkbox"]').checked = true;
        return false;

      });
  });
</script>